[SPEAKER_00] Top.

645
00:45:56,000 --> 00:45:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Završi se utaknica.

646
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Super.

647
00:45:58,000 --> 00:45:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve, super.

648
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je zaboravljeno.

649
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je zaboravljeno.

650
00:46:01,000 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] I šta napravimo?

651
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odam opet u funtanu.

652
00:46:03,000 --> 00:46:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta će, Draganič?

653
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad nisam sam, nego cijela ekipa.

654
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se utvrde gradimo.

655
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se utvrde gradimo.

656
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da se utvrde gradimo.

657
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[UNKNOWN] Tako je.

658
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prama tome, eto ti kakvi u životu imaš situacije.

659
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, znam da su komentari bili navijača i to onih…

660
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, to sam ja.

661
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] To sam ja.

662
00:46:20,000 --> 00:46:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iskreni to sam ja i kad pogrešim kažemo prosti i kad… to sam ja.

663
00:46:24,000 --> 00:46:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim, ono, jedino što je nekakva naša zadaća u životu je bilo da budemo mi.

664
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

665
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da svako nađe nekakva svoj put i da budemo ono što je.

666
00:46:33,000 --> 00:46:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bez nekakvih maski.

667
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

668
00:46:35,000 --> 00:46:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prima tome, nisam falš, ne želim biti falš.

669
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad me treba kazni, treba me kazni. Kad napravim glupost, napravim glupost.

670
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ispričam se.

671
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ja se vratim na teren.

672
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bari se trudim vratim na terenu.

673
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Eto.

674
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Najpored tehničkih i taktičkih, kao goto, hoćeš karakteristika koje si imao…

675
00:46:57,000 --> 00:47:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zarazna je bila ta energija, taj pobednički duh koji si ti zapravo sebe ispromovirao u lidera.

676
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:10,000
